17_5	0.12125435	This fresh round of investigations into the long-ago killings, many of which had been ignored by authorities for years, was inspired by the well-publicized conviction in 1994 of an aging white defendant in the 1963 assassination of the Mississippi civil rights leader Medgar Evers.
